{
  "stem": "20088.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 30.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So you can imagine what a feeling that was when I realized that a huge rat was kind of trying to eat my feet.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and another terrible incident was-- that was still when there were more people at night-- we had at the end of each barrack in winter, they put a bucket so that we didn't have to go to the toilet so far to this one block where there was a toilet.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but if it was full, we had to empty it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The one who was last and it was full had to take this bucket in the night to this place and empty it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was, of course, terrible job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, people left it so full that when you did carry it, it all spilled over.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it took a long time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so everybody tried to avoid that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so once somebody had emptied it-- instead of taking it, they had emptied it outside just in the back of the barrack.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the kapo had seen that in the morning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was, again, a full bucket, but they'd seen the mess which was outside.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she came in, called us out all-- we had to get up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we all stood in front of our beds, and she shouted and said, again, you dirty Jews and [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was an expression and [GERMAN] and, you know, terrible swearing they did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, look what you've done.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can't even carry your own shit and blah, blah blah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she called somebody and gave her a muck and said, throw this all on you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then you will see how you behave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to empty all this stuff on-- throw it on all the inmates.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
